Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is Takasu here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji got sick and was hospitalized right before New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's still at home sick right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? Isn't that serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I should go and visit him later{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I ended up sleeping through the whole winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How should I face her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was rejected... wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's the only explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Why did you close it again all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Get out here! Hey, Tai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, you're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The noodles are soggy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're eating junk food again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since you're so annoying, I'll eat it right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've cooked for you every single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why haven't you come over since New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't get mad at me just because Minorin rejected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm just frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not like I want you to pity me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just treat me like you usually do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm doing this for the sake of you and Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why am I so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said I'd support Minorin, but I always just crash at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's only natural for her to misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you think that's why she rejected me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think she just doesn't feel that w{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I think Minorin likes you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but she probably thinks I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about you? Do you really think Minorin doesn't like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I get the feeling she's kind of interested in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't come over anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't need your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't need to wake me up every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll try my best by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you still feel the same about Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure she'll change her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why you should do what you should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't run away from Minorin! You have to confirm her true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}don't burn down your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I promise I won't use the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hereby declare I'll only eat fast food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, I wonder how long you'll last.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll last, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't run away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan, you forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I even stamped it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stamped?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That Okinawa thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you're really going to Okinawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's great! That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This isn't the time for me to care about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I see Kushieda, the first thing I'll do is greet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll start from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to return this to you as soon as possible since it looked really expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, I traded you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}this was in the pocket the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't end up needing it that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The sea! The sun! Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Herbal wine! Chinsuko! Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Six days and five nights in Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? You're by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's weird. Where's Taka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}God knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga! Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}P-Penis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taka-chan, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga is going to bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's because you were bothering me with your Chinsuko crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll take it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How does it look on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ow! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is still Ryuuji's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:40.02,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ow! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see you guys are all hyped up for the new semester!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}'Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good morning, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}G{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}G-G{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to buy some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Class is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did I run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wish everything would just burn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It burned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, the field trip won't be canceled,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll go as planned, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss, I don't understand what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The hotel we were going to stay at in Okinawa burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The field trip will now be a ski trip for three days and two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow! It's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?! That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not like I burned the hotel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Objection! This is nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn it! Why is Ami-chan late on a day like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If Ami-chan were here, she'd definitely have a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kawashima-san was modeling in Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's couldn't make it back for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But since she's already spent a lot of time in the southern islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}she'd probably want to go to a snowy mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Going home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What happened to Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You guys aren't together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, Taiga said she had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I'll try my best by myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}If you still feel the same about Minorin,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's even living on cup noodles for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That girl was really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's probably a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kawashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aren't you supposed to be working in Hawaii?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you please go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can you be picking a fight when we haven't even seen each other recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hate you because you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.96,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We were supposed to meet ten minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't be so picky, stupid Chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here, this is what you were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you guys are already friendly enough to exchange gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I paid for it, so it's not actually a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, this is useless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll just wear it when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aren't you going to take it with you to Okinawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The field trip is now a ski trip for three days and two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They said the hotel in Okinawa burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.86,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have something to tell you before the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen up, don't hang around Ryuuji during the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'd bother {\i1}me{\i0} to hang around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, Ryuuji was rejected by Minorin on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Actually, it was right before I was going to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She rejected me by hinting that I shouldn't confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See, you got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, Minorin likes Ryuuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but for some reason, things aren't moving along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll have exams once we're seniors, and we'll be in different classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This field trip is his last chance to confirm Minorin's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You got that, stupid Chihuahua?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm fine with it if you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was a boring conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hopefully you're the {\i1}only{\i0} one getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone as stupid as you could never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, why are you following me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to go this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never thought you'd go that far for Kushieda and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... So... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll do my best on the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perhaps confirming Kushieda's feelings would be a waste of effort, but{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stupid! You and Minorin like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey... Where did you get all that confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a reason to believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're capable of becoming Minori's lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, I'm going to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a new convenience store there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was with that attitude today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't run away tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I don't move forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}'Mornin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... About yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How should I put it... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It wasn't even on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then, I'm going first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to take care of this since you got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the heck is wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn that Taiga, damn that Taiga, damn that{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:57.75,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I'm totally all right with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, let me hold a side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, your hair looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I cut the front a bit shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Actually, I wanted to cut it so short that even berries could grow on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, like a guy's hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always had a buzz cut when I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I would just sit at the barber's with my younger brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and they'd just rip my hair off with clippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My nickname back then was "Mr. Lady."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm surprised that you noticed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, that's because I always look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow, what a shocking confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right, I have to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of which, your brother plays high school baseball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, his school is a frequent visitor of the Koshien.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow, I'd be proud of him if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be honest, I'm a bit jealous of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ami-senpai, happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good morning, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you see Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I didn't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How should I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's really "oh my."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean by "oh my"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder what I meant... What did I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, the groups for the field trip are decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't you think this grouping is really weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You, Ami, Kashii, Aisaka, Kushieda, Takasu, Noto, Haruta and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a mixture of nine boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since we have more girls, I think this is a good grouping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}B-But you and Taiga will be{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Never mind! But if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're not happy about it, go join another group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up, Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're annoying, that's why I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How could you tell me to shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:10.09,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you don't want to, you can go join{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said that's not the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See, even Master Kitamura said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Buzz off, Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you have to say such things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? We need to make a guidebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, each group needs to turn it in by next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do we have to do something so troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think it'd be easier if we worked together on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How about my place on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, my place is pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-Isn't this place a bit over the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder how much the rent is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu, do you live next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, you live in this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I live in an apartment next to this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I brought a few examples from previous field trips for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are guides inside these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As expected of a master! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll go make some black tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I also brought some madeleines over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka, I need to use the computer, where's the outlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Behind the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, you can talk to Kitamura normally now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You shouldn't really care about it, just go help Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda, let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Golgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not Golgo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I am Golgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't stand behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm the one behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Never mind then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's weird that there's usable tableware in Taiga's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The last time I came here was in freshman year, so I had the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This must be thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I haven't been doing anything lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga did this all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The reason she's able to do it is because you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You haven't been here since freshman year?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, because of the stuff with her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since then, I wouldn't come here unless I had a reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was afraid of failing, so I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You did a good job, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You weren't afraid of failing, and you stepped in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you think it'd be all right if we just copied this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why would we copy an Okinawa guide when we're going to a snowy mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh my, we can't show Yuusaku this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think you should worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're just making me more curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow, I guess it must be a big shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just a picture, but that magnificent rejection{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid Chihuahua!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? Blame the person who brought this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.65,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, tea's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.69,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, be nice to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Actually, I'm kind of looking forward to this field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I mean, it's the last time our class will be doing something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This class is really fun. I'll be lonely without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only we could stay like this forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only we could stay like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda, me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}staying like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She actually sorted them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right, I can't stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to confirm Kushieda's true feelings on the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ni-Ni-Ni-Nigauri (Bitter melon).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ri-Ri-Ri-Richiumu Denchi (Lithium battery).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chinome (Blood blister).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Meidosan no hesonogoma (A maid's belly button fluff).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mandoragora no benishuuga (Mandrake red pickled ginger).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu, start with "ga."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ganbaru (Do your best)!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The subject is bitter things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Actually, wasted effort is "bitter" in a sense, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next, start with "ru."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ru... Ru... Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:56.52,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Sukyatto suru Nigamigawa Shibuhiko (Scat-singing Nigamigawa Shibuhiko)!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:57.69,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Who the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right, I have to do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and deliver those rejected feelings from Christmas to her once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to confess again,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}even if it's for the sake of Taiga who's supporting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really no good; I don't say what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.91,0:23:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've had enough.
